fields.description: Address inside MFC from where item was supposed to be picked.
fields.name: address

fields.description: Quantity that was picked during the session. Always 0 for not picked event.
fields.name: amount

fields.description: List of actual barcodes that was scanned during picking session. Empty list for not picked event.
fields.name: barcodes

fields.description: MFC location id where picking session was performed.
fields.name: location_id

fields.description: Id of the order for what item was picked.
fields.name: order_id

fields.description: Timestamp when message was published to topic.
fields.name: pubsub_publish_time

fields.description: Id of the tote to where item was picked. Can be `null` for not picked event.
fields.name: tote_id
